data.description: MOTIVATED SELLER*WILL CONTRIBUTE CLOSING COSTS TO BUYER* Welcome to your dream home! This exquisite property, crafted by Richmond American Homes in 2019, perfectly blends modern elegance and comfort. With 1816 SQ FT, 4 BD & 2 BR, it provides ample space for your family's needs. The open floor plan invites natural light to flow seamlessly, creating a warm and inviting ambiance. Situated on a generous corner lot, you'll have plenty of outdoor space for relaxation and entertainment. Nestled in the coveted neighborhood of Rolling Hills, residents can access a wealth of amenities, including a resident's club with a zero-entry swimming pool featuring lap lanes and an exhilarating water slide, tennis courts & volleyball courts.
